Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: DEX payouts are revshares from the DEXfees

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: value in DEX should be -in part- an extrapolation of future expected revenue streams from DEX revshares

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: so the more people are bullish on DEX trading volume, the higher dex price

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: also only 1M DEX total supply, everytime 1M USD in trading fees is accumulated, payout to DEX holders in KMD üôÇ

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: Anyway, DEX value is somewhat pegged to usd value because of above, so KMD/USD drops, but DEX/USD stays the same -> DEX/KMD goes up

Author: Cryptoon#3362
Content: apart from organic DEX value growth offcourse üôÇ
